==Abstract==

This IIP describes the getblocktemplate RPC for mining pool and solo mining software. It implements BIP 22 for INTcoin.

==Motivation==

getblocktemplate provides:
* Decentralized block construction (miners choose transactions)
* Efficient work distribution for pools
* Transparency in block contents

==Specification==

===Request===

<pre>
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "getblocktemplate",
  "params": [{"rules": ["csv", "segwit"]}],
  "id": 1
}
</pre>

===Response===

<pre>
{
  "version": 536870912,
  "previousblockhash": "00000...",
  "transactions": [
    {
      "data": "01000000...",
      "txid": "abc123...",
      "hash": "abc123...",
      "depends": [],
      "fee": 10000,
      "sigops": 1,
      "weight": 800
    }
  ],
  "coinbaseaux": {},
  "coinbasevalue": 1051136360000,
  "target": "00000...",
  "mintime": 1773014400,
  "mutable": ["time", "transactions", "prevblock"],
  "noncerange": "00000000ffffffff",
  "sigoplimit": 80000,
  "sizelimit": 4000000,
  "weightlimit": 16000000,
  "curtime": 1773014500,
  "bits": "1f040000",
  "height": 1
}
</pre>

===Block Submission===

<pre>
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "submitblock",
  "params": ["<hex-encoded-block>"],
  "id": 1
}
</pre>

===INTcoin Specifics===

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! INTcoin Value
|-
| Block size limit || 4,000,000 bytes
|-
| Weight limit || 16,000,000 WU
|-
| PoW algorithm || RandomX v2
|-
| Coinbase maturity || 100 blocks
|}

===RandomX Integration===

Mining software must:
# Initialize RandomX with epoch key
# Hash block header using RandomX
# Compare hash to target

<pre>
epoch_key = "INTcoin-RandomX-Epoch-" + str(height / 2048)
randomx_init(epoch_key)
hash = randomx_hash(block_header)
if hash <= target:
    submit_block(block)
</pre>

